{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"70946d2a-56e1-460d-b135-40fa54a31ce5","content":"`.testsettings` is a legacy format **not supported by MSTest v3+**. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's what your file configures and how to migrate each part:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Assembly resolution / deployment | `<DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| Code coverage data collector | `<DataCollector>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01PPxgGE1ETEWgAsz9WArPhB","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating .runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01H9Gg1HmXtRRrBB8v1juQyk","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-7f05a3500ff94af987c5a10b9bca69f6/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <DeploymentEnabled>true</DeploymentEnabled>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=b03f5f7f11d50a3a\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage>\n            <ModulePaths>\n              <Exclude>\n                <ModulePath>.*tests\\.dll$</ModulePath>\n              </Exclude>\n            </ModulePaths>\n          </CodeCoverage>\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-7f05a3500ff94af987c5a10b9bca69f6/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"b8ee791d-69d4-4829-9350-6bf7fcee4336","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext=\"true\"`\n2. Test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. Code coverage data collector\n\nThey've upgraded to MSTest 3.8.0 which uses the modern MSTest runner. The `.testsettings` format is legacy and not supported by the modern runner — they need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file.\n\nLet me create a `.runsettings` file that captures the equivalent configuration.","outputTokens":710,"requestId":"CFCC:1CA5E9:611F77B:6D2B0D0:69EC25BC"},"id":"eab68cf1-fd2e-4e8a-91bd-c639cb8546ea","timestamp":"2026-04-25T02:24:08.680Z","parentId":"f59c0a5e-1b91-4667-b126-353d62a3994f"}
